---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ServiceSchema from '../components/ServiceSchema.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Bulk Earthworks | Surrey Contracting Limited"
  description="Bulk earthworks and excavation across Surrey, large-scale excavation, site levelling, land clearance and land remediation."
  path="/earthworks"
  active="services"
>
  <ServiceSchema slot="head" name="Bulk Earthworks" slug="earthworks" description="Bulk earthworks and excavation across Surrey, large-scale excavation, site levelling, land clearance and land remediation." />

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-bg" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="page-hero-img" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/bulk-earthworks.jpg')"></div>
    <div class="page-hero-vignette"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="container page-hero-inner">
    <nav class="crumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="12" height="12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M9 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg>
      <a href="/services">Services</a>
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="12" height="12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M9 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg>
      <span>Bulk Earthworks</span>
    </nav>
    <h1 class="page-title">Bulk Earthworks</h1>
    <p class="page-lede">Bulk earthworks and excavation across Surrey, large-scale excavation, site levelling, land clearance and land remediation.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="page-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Bulk Earthworks</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Residential and commercial earthmoving, expertly delivered.</h2>
      <p class="section-lede">Surrey Contracting is a trusted and experienced earthworks and excavation contractor operating across Surrey, London and the South East. We carry out bulk excavation and earthworks using the latest equipment to clear, level and prepare your site quickly and efficiently for any construction project. Whether you need to level your site or have a complete cut and fill project completed, Surrey Contracting can provide solutions for projects of all sizes and complexities.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="svc-detail">
  <div class="container svc-detail-grid">
    <div class="svc-detail-media">
      <div class="svc-detail-photo" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/bulk-earthworks.jpg')"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-detail-copy">
      <h2 class="section-title">Bulk Earthworks</h2>
      <p class="lede-dark">Bulk earthworks, or otherwise known as cut and fill, involve the removal, moving or adding of large quantities of soil or rock from one area to another to make the land suitable for building. Surrey Contracting has the expertise and equipment to carry out bulk earthworks for any type of construction project. We can handle any ground conditions and challenges, using the latest equipment and machinery. We comply with all environmental and safety regulations, and we dispose of and recycle waste material responsibly. Whether you need bulk earthworks for a new-build development, a commercial site or a residential property, we provide a fast, efficient and professional service.</p>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>Cut &amp; fill to levels</li>
        <li>Topsoil management &amp; stockpiling</li>
        <li>Ground remediation</li>
        <li>Environmental compliance</li>
        <li>Waste recycling &amp; disposal</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="svc-detail svc-detail-alt">
  <div class="container svc-detail-grid svc-detail-reverse">
    <div class="svc-detail-media">
      <div class="svc-detail-photo" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/services/earthworks-excavations.jpg')"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-detail-copy">
      <h2 class="section-title">Lakes, Ponds &amp; Swimming Pools</h2>
      <p class="lede-dark">We specialise in bulk excavation works. Whether it's for a new swimming pool or adjustments to an existing lake or pond, we can provide a complete solution from start to finish. We have a fleet of excavators and dumpers that can handle any scale of excavation, from small domestic gardens to large multi-phase developments, and our skilled operators perform the work safely, accurately and on schedule.</p>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>Large-scale excavation</li>
        <li>Multi-phase developments</li>
        <li>Fleet of excavators &amp; dumpers</li>
        <li>Accurate level control</li>
        <li>Aggregate supply</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="svc-detail">
  <div class="container svc-detail-grid">
    <div class="svc-detail-media">
      <div class="svc-detail-photo" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/services/earthworks-clearance.jpg')"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-detail-copy">
      <h2 class="section-title">Land Clearance</h2>
      <p class="lede-dark">Surrey Contracting offers a comprehensive land clearance service, removing any existing structures, rubbish, vegetation or debris from the site. Land clearance is often necessary before any construction or landscaping project can begin, to ensure a safe and clean working area. We have the specialised machinery and equipment to carry out land clearance of any size and complexity. We work with both domestic and commercial clients, and we can tailor our land clearance service to suit your needs and budget. All waste is segregated on site and disposed of or recycled responsibly.</p>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>Structure removal</li>
        <li>Vegetation clearance</li>
        <li>Waste segregation</li>
        <li>Domestic &amp; commercial</li>
        <li>Responsible disposal</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="svc-detail svc-detail-alt">
  <div class="container svc-detail-grid svc-detail-reverse">
    <div class="svc-detail-media">
      <div class="svc-detail-photo" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/services/earthworks-levelling.jpg')"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-detail-copy">
      <h2 class="section-title">Land &amp; Site Levelling</h2>
      <p class="lede-dark">We provide high-quality land levelling services, the process of flattening or adjusting existing slopes and undulations to create a level surface. Land levelling is often required for construction, landscaping or agricultural purposes, to improve the performance and appearance of the land. We use advanced surveying and engineering methods to ensure accuracy and precision. Surrey Contracting has the expertise and equipment to carry out land levelling for any type of project, from garden re-grading to large development platforms.</p>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>Slope adjustment</li>
        <li>Development platforms</li>
        <li>Garden re-grading</li>
        <li>Surveying &amp; engineering</li>
        <li>Agricultural levelling</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-strip">
  <div class="container cta-strip-row">
    <div>
      <h3>Got an earthworks project to discuss?</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-strip-ctas">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-yellow">Request a quote</a>
      <a href="tel:01932932650" class="btn btn-ghost-light">01932 932650</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</BaseLayout>
